OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start, perhaps some
OL,6,Flight morning rain. Largely dry by
OL,7,Fmidday, with sunny intervals
OL,8,Fdeveloping from the north through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. A brisk northeasterly wind,
OL,10,Fstrong near coasts, feeling cool.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with evening sunny spells
OL,13,Fas winds ease. A clear and cold night,
OL,14,Fwith light winds and frost patches.
OL,15,FCloud increasing from the north late
OL,16,Fin the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
