OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloudy, with rain through the
OL,6,Fmorning, then largely dry and bright
OL,7,Fwith sunny intervals and a few coastal
OL,8,Fshowers later. Breezy, though strong
OL,9,Fwinds near coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBreezy
OL,12,Fbut bright start Tuesday, then
OL,13,Fincreasingly cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain. Blustery showers, with possible
OL,15,Fthunder, and some sunny intervals
OL,16,FWednesday and Thursday. Cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
